$name[] = "Informational Magnetism";
$slide[] = "
<UL>
<LI>View \"pointwise mutual information\" as a force acting between two atoms
of data, whatever they might be</LI>
<LI>Sum up all the forces acting on a particular atom to determing its net
attraction or repulsion</LI>
<LI>Fill in the empty slots in a template sentence by inserting the most
strongly attracted word</LI>
<LI>Each inserted word acts as an additional constraint, exterting a force on
all filled slots</LI>
<LI>This may cause previously inserted words to pop out and be replaced</LI>
<LI>The generation eventually stabilises</LI>
</UL>
";

